WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-

2
00:00:12.720 --> 00:00:14.900
Dunno where my
ticket outta here went.

3
00:00:14.980 --> 00:00:17.570
And there's no time to look for it.

4
00:00:17.650 --> 00:00:21.840
My only options now are
to beat them or die trying.

5
00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:31.010
Stamina's at its limit and I
can't use two of my best skills!

6
00:00:33.240 --> 00:00:36.110
But I won't give up. I refuse.

7
00:00:38.040 --> 00:00:39.210
I...

8
00:00:39.290 --> 00:00:41.520
am going to survive!

9
00:00:48.930 --> 00:00:52.600
If anyone knows what it's
like at the bottom. it's me.

10
00:00:52.680 --> 00:00:56.590
But I could never stop
striving to climb higher!

11
00:01:08.990 --> 00:01:12.890
Well. they call him the
weakest hunter of all mankind.

12
00:01:15.540 --> 00:01:18.560
Wait. really? That's a thing?

13
00:01:19.820 --> 00:01:24.290
It was once he got hospitalized
after a trip through an E-Rank gate.

14
00:01:24.370 --> 00:01:27.200
If that isn't weak.
then I don't know what is.

15
00:01:28.720 --> 00:01:30.840
You're done. So give up.

16
00:01:30.920 --> 00:01:32.840
Stop now before you break. kid.

17
00:01:32.920 --> 00:01:34.730
Listen to Mister Song.

18
00:01:34.810 --> 00:01:37.460
You push yourself way too hard.

19
00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:42.920
You deserve this.

20
00:01:46.490 --> 00:01:50.360
Now why did you go and
do something so dangerous?

21
00:01:50.440 --> 00:01:54.320
I know. you were at the bottom.
But you've come so far.

22
00:01:54.400 --> 00:01:58.210
That should have been
enough. don't you think?

23
00:01:58.290 --> 00:01:59.810
Jinwoo?

24
00:03:32.880 --> 00:03:35.560
I missed the third raid.

25
00:03:35.640 --> 00:03:39.270
Unfortunately. I was no longer
fit for combat by that time.

26
00:03:39.350 --> 00:03:42.220
My body couldn't keep up anymore.

27
00:03:42.300 --> 00:03:44.600
Did you take part
in the third raid at all?

28
00:03:44.680 --> 00:03:49.190
Yes. I acted as a point
of contact for security. sir.

29
00:03:49.270 --> 00:03:53.900
That dungeon break claimed a great many
lives. and those who did manage to escape

30
00:03:53.980 --> 00:03:56.770
carry the mental scars from it still.

31
00:03:57.530 --> 00:04:01.100
Though I suppose
every hunter has similar scars.

32
00:04:02.120 --> 00:04:06.670
And if they can't overcome that
harsh pain. then all that awaits...

33
00:04:06.750 --> 00:04:08.610
is destruction.

34
00:04:09.920 --> 00:04:12.250
Kinda hard to believe this is me.

35
00:04:12.330 --> 00:04:14.130
I mean look at you.

36
00:04:14.210 --> 00:04:16.720
Taller. more muscular.

37
00:04:16.800 --> 00:04:18.930
You look strong.

38
00:04:19.010 --> 00:04:21.810
But I guess it's only your
appearance that's changed.

39
00:04:21.890 --> 00:04:23.890
Dig deeper. and you're still weak.

40
00:04:23.970 --> 00:04:26.380
Hell. you're right at death's door.

41
00:04:31.270 --> 00:04:33.480
E-Rank hunter. Jinwoo Sung.

42
00:04:33.560 --> 00:04:36.160
That's all you'll ever be.

43
00:04:36.240 --> 00:04:39.240
A dreamer who never
learned his place.

44
00:04:39.320 --> 00:04:40.930
Shut your mouth!

45
00:04:54.250 --> 00:04:57.720
So pathetic. All that talk
about how "ready you are"

46
00:04:57.800 --> 00:05:00.100
and this is the best you could do?

47
00:05:00.180 --> 00:05:04.280
You'll have nothing to blame
for your death but your own ego.

48
00:05:05.390 --> 00:05:08.610
This all feels so...

49
00:05:08.690 --> 00:05:10.500
familiar.

50
00:05:12.730 --> 00:05:16.260
I can't remember. what happened next?

51
00:05:18.450 --> 00:05:20.260
The quest.

52
00:05:23.700 --> 00:05:26.360
Guess luck's one of your skills. too.

53
00:05:27.040 --> 00:05:31.210
Seems like they've decided it
would be a waste to let you die here.

54
00:05:31.290 --> 00:05:33.270
Till next time.

55
00:05:44.840 --> 00:05:49.790
This is the penalty zone.

56
00:05:51.140 --> 00:05:52.520
Oh. yeah.

57
00:05:52.600 --> 00:05:55.210
I didn't get around
to the daily quest.

58
00:05:57.650 --> 00:05:59.640
It must be past midnight.

59
00:06:02.360 --> 00:06:06.000
Good timing.
This penalty saved my life.

60
00:06:06.080 --> 00:06:08.210
No wonder it wished me luck.

61
00:06:08.290 --> 00:06:10.920
I wouldn't have survived
that mess without it.

62
00:06:11.000 --> 00:06:15.050
Or was the system cheering
me on because it wants me alive?

63
00:06:15.130 --> 00:06:17.010
Who knows?

64
00:06:17.090 --> 00:06:18.740
Shop.

65
00:06:20.420 --> 00:06:23.160
First time my fatigue went over ninety.

66
00:06:32.640 --> 00:06:36.320
I guess potions won't restore
my HP if I'm seriously injured.

67
00:06:36.400 --> 00:06:42.090
I can either wait to heal naturally
or try to get restored by leveling up.

68
00:06:43.690 --> 00:06:47.270
Okay then.
Leveling up it is. I guess.

69
00:06:51.740 --> 00:06:53.830
Till next time. he said.

70
00:06:53.910 --> 00:06:58.260
Meaning. If I live long
enough I'll see him again!

71
00:06:58.340 --> 00:07:02.130
Any pain I go through.
any suffering I endure.

72
00:07:02.210 --> 00:07:06.250
if it doesn't kill me.
it'll make me stronger.

73
00:07:20.320 --> 00:07:23.670
That was a weird dream.

74
00:07:25.740 --> 00:07:28.830
Jinwoo isn't home yet? Huh?

75
00:07:28.910 --> 00:07:32.290
No way is he doing
a raid this late. right?

76
00:07:32.370 --> 00:07:36.530
If I didn't know better. I'd
think he got himself a girl.

77
00:07:38.420 --> 00:07:42.010
Hope he remembers my
guardian-teacher conference.

78
00:07:42.090 --> 00:07:44.650
And that he'll actually
make it there.

79
00:07:50.050 --> 00:07:52.950
Nice to kill two
birds with one stone.

80
00:07:53.970 --> 00:07:56.480
Ten minutes till I return
to the job change quest.

81
00:07:56.560 --> 00:08:00.560
so. I should probably use
this time to sort out my gear.

82
00:08:03.610 --> 00:08:05.090
Buy.

83
00:08:09.780 --> 00:08:11.080
"Knight Killer."

84
00:08:11.160 --> 00:08:14.580
This thing deals twenty-five percent
more damage to armor types. huh?

85
00:08:14.660 --> 00:08:17.000
It's a little pricy
but should be worth it.

86
00:08:17.080 --> 00:08:19.630
And that. leaves the rune stone.

87
00:08:19.710 --> 00:08:22.420
Not sure what it is.
but it's gotta be handy.

88
00:08:22.500 --> 00:08:25.320
It is a "Ruler's Hand" after all.

89
00:08:37.190 --> 00:08:42.520
Let's see here.
It doesn't need mana? Nice.

90
00:08:42.600 --> 00:08:46.100
I can manipulate objects
without ever touching them?

91
00:08:47.280 --> 00:08:49.140
Like he did.

92
00:08:54.820 --> 00:08:58.230
I'll have to up my proficiency
to move something big.

93
00:08:59.870 --> 00:09:02.730
I've prepared myself as best I can.

94
00:09:05.090 --> 00:09:08.330
The rest will come down to luck.

95
00:09:15.560 --> 00:09:19.420
I see you invited a few
more friends to the party.

96
00:09:25.360 --> 00:09:28.660
Guild master. We'll arrive
at Jeju Island soon.

97
00:09:28.740 --> 00:09:30.530
Understood.

98
00:09:30.610 --> 00:09:34.160
Sorry. Miss Cha. I know how
painful this entire ordeal must be.

99
00:09:34.240 --> 00:09:36.830
No. I'm fine.
But thank you. sir.

100
00:09:36.910 --> 00:09:40.170
I wasn't a hunter during the
third raid. but I can empathize

101
00:09:40.250 --> 00:09:41.790
with how you must be feeling.

102
00:09:41.870 --> 00:09:44.920
That's why I'm glad to help.
I really am.

103
00:09:45.000 --> 00:09:46.930
I appreciate you saying that.

104
00:09:47.010 --> 00:09:50.720
Mana's been found. Several
sources in the water beneath us!

105
00:09:50.800 --> 00:09:52.560
Bringing up the feed!

106
00:09:56.020 --> 00:09:57.500
What the?

107
00:10:02.520 --> 00:10:04.270
Knew this knife was worth it!

108
00:10:04.350 --> 00:10:06.660
Much better than fist fighting!

109
00:10:06.740 --> 00:10:07.740
But...

110
00:10:07.820 --> 00:10:09.280
Something feels off.

111
00:10:09.360 --> 00:10:11.990
No matter how many enemies I kill.

112
00:10:12.070 --> 00:10:14.160
I'm not gaining any XP.

113
00:10:14.240 --> 00:10:15.370
Plus.

114
00:10:15.450 --> 00:10:17.710
Their mages haven't done a thing.

115
00:10:17.790 --> 00:10:20.790
They've been casting.
but nothing's happened.

116
00:10:20.870 --> 00:10:24.850
The knights are the only ones
attacking. so what are they doing?

117
00:10:26.050 --> 00:10:27.510
It's summoning magic!

118
00:10:27.590 --> 00:10:31.070
The knights are just weapons
they've been calling through the gates.

119
00:10:32.130 --> 00:10:35.270
That also explains
why I'm not leveling up!

120
00:10:35.350 --> 00:10:39.580
'Cause the ones I should
be targeting are the mages!

121
00:10:45.730 --> 00:10:46.900
I was right.

122
00:10:46.980 --> 00:10:49.260
So let's do this.

123
00:10:49.980 --> 00:10:51.970
One mage down.

124
00:10:53.070 --> 00:10:54.720
Five left.

125
00:10:58.160 --> 00:11:00.230
Make that four.

126
00:11:16.640 --> 00:11:19.620
Enough of this. Get over here!

127
00:11:25.180 --> 00:11:26.920
Three more.

128
00:11:33.270 --> 00:11:35.050
A golem?

129
00:11:50.710 --> 00:11:53.380
They thought one heavyweight
would win it for them.

130
00:11:53.460 --> 00:11:57.200
but fewer targets
just makes it easier for me!

131
00:12:14.230 --> 00:12:16.740
Your summoners are already dead. so.

132
00:12:16.820 --> 00:12:20.250
Why don't you...

133
00:12:20.330 --> 00:12:22.930
join them in hell?!

134
00:12:49.650 --> 00:12:53.630
I think I won. but what's that mean?

135
00:12:54.600 --> 00:13:00.280
Will I be able to switch to a more advanced
class with the points this quest got me?

136
00:13:00.360 --> 00:13:05.340
If so. I imagine it's gonna
be based on my performance.

137
00:13:05.420 --> 00:13:07.820
I won't get to choose.

138
00:13:15.680 --> 00:13:18.410
I'm not really following.

139
00:13:32.600 --> 00:13:37.200
"Shadow army?" What? What the?

140
00:13:37.280 --> 00:13:38.450
No.

141
00:13:38.530 --> 00:13:40.660
This doesn't make any sense.

142
00:13:40.740 --> 00:13:43.660
That's my new job class?

143
00:13:43.740 --> 00:13:45.330
Necromancer?

144
00:13:45.410 --> 00:13:49.210
What the hell? My intellect stat
is the one that I ignore the most!

145
00:13:49.290 --> 00:13:51.110
So how did I?

146
00:13:51.750 --> 00:13:57.140
Necromancers are a magic-type class
that summon undead monsters as servants.

147
00:13:57.220 --> 00:13:59.720
But I'm an assassin build.

148
00:13:59.800 --> 00:14:05.160
My main stat is strength. and I use
daggers with a close-range combat style.

149
00:14:06.520 --> 00:14:11.770
A back-line class like
necromancer will waste all of that!

150
00:14:11.850 --> 00:14:15.490
Oh. uh. I can say no?

151
00:14:15.570 --> 00:14:19.860
The benefits aren't clear.
Maybe I should pass.

152
00:14:19.940 --> 00:14:21.680
Decline.

153
00:14:22.530 --> 00:14:25.140
Wait. a hidden class?

154
00:14:30.750 --> 00:14:34.100
Does it have some
kind of special power?

155
00:14:36.010 --> 00:14:37.720
Necromancy.

156
00:14:37.800 --> 00:14:40.610
If I had some kinda
frame of reference.

157
00:14:43.760 --> 00:14:45.520
Summoning magic!

158
00:14:45.600 --> 00:14:48.850
These mages were just
showing me a little sample.

159
00:14:48.930 --> 00:14:53.310
It wasn't necromancy specifically.
but it was close enough.

160
00:14:53.390 --> 00:14:58.800
And my opponents. they all had
abilities I'd seen in previous fights.

161
00:14:59.780 --> 00:15:02.860
The system made this
job-change quest seem optional.

162
00:15:02.940 --> 00:15:06.410
But maybe. it was inevitable.

163
00:15:06.490 --> 00:15:08.790
I see where this is going.

164
00:15:08.870 --> 00:15:11.210
The mages weren't
strong on their own.

165
00:15:11.290 --> 00:15:17.530
But I am. and there's no rule that says
necromancers can't fight on the front lines.

166
00:15:17.610 --> 00:15:23.300
If classes work likes stats. then
as I level up. my skills will. too.

167
00:15:23.380 --> 00:15:26.710
and my shadow army
will become stronger.

168
00:15:27.390 --> 00:15:29.020
In other words.

169
00:15:29.100 --> 00:15:32.040
I won't be solo leveling anymore!

170
00:15:32.760 --> 00:15:34.330
Accept.

171
00:15:40.080 --> 00:15:42.280
-Here.
-Thank you.

172
00:15:46.530 --> 00:15:48.580
We really stayed up till dawn.

173
00:15:48.660 --> 00:15:52.410
Hunter Choi's crew should be
making landfall on the island by now.

174
00:15:52.490 --> 00:15:53.870
Right.

175
00:15:53.950 --> 00:15:55.370
Sorry I kept you.

176
00:15:55.450 --> 00:15:56.800
It's fine.

177
00:15:56.880 --> 00:16:01.740
But since you're here. would you
mind humoring me for a bit. Jinchul?

178
00:17:00.400 --> 00:17:02.070
"Shadow monarch?"

179
00:17:02.150 --> 00:17:04.650
I got an instant upgrade?

180
00:17:04.730 --> 00:17:07.660
Must've scored a lot of bonus points.

181
00:17:07.740 --> 00:17:12.780
Unique class skills and ten
ability points. plus a new title.

182
00:17:12.860 --> 00:17:17.340
If my rewards are ready.
is the quest finally over?

183
00:17:17.420 --> 00:17:20.400
Did I complete the job change?

184
00:17:22.580 --> 00:17:25.970
I hear cries from those
broken bits of armor.

185
00:17:26.050 --> 00:17:28.370
They sound like people in pain.

186
00:17:29.340 --> 00:17:31.530
Shadow Extraction.

187
00:17:32.380 --> 00:17:34.660
A command word. huh?

188
00:17:38.690 --> 00:17:40.210
Arise.

189
00:17:58.790 --> 00:18:00.810
Look at that. Damn.

190
00:18:01.460 --> 00:18:05.640
The unique skills are Shadow
Extraction and Shadow Storage.

191
00:18:05.720 --> 00:18:08.470
One lets me drain mana
to create shadow soldiers.

192
00:18:08.550 --> 00:18:12.890
and the other lets me hold those
soldiers to summon whenever.

193
00:18:12.970 --> 00:18:16.400
Then. these must be my soldiers.

194
00:18:16.480 --> 00:18:18.810
The extraction can
fail based on the strength

195
00:18:18.890 --> 00:18:22.230
of the target
and the time since death.

196
00:18:22.310 --> 00:18:24.020
Gotta be careful then.

197
00:18:24.100 --> 00:18:26.200
I got mages and knights.

198
00:18:26.280 --> 00:18:28.640
They come in different ranks. too.

199
00:18:30.860 --> 00:18:35.920
If it's possible to extract A or S-Rank
shadows. and their power level reflects

200
00:18:36.000 --> 00:18:38.290
how strong they were in life.

201
00:18:38.370 --> 00:18:40.020
Then.

202
00:18:47.590 --> 00:18:49.340
Hell yeah.

203
00:18:49.420 --> 00:18:55.110
Since I have a limit to my storage.
I'll release eleven of the infantry.

204
00:18:56.640 --> 00:18:59.080
Sorry I woke you up for nothing.

205
00:18:59.770 --> 00:19:01.060
Now. then.

206
00:19:01.140 --> 00:19:03.920
Knight Commander Igris the Bloodred.

207
00:19:04.000 --> 00:19:06.550
Will you submit to my control?

208
00:19:07.610 --> 00:19:09.470
Arise.

209
00:19:18.290 --> 00:19:19.810
What?

210
00:19:22.200 --> 00:19:25.270
Right. it told me there's
a chance it could fail.

211
00:19:25.920 --> 00:19:28.030
Two more tries.

212
00:19:32.000 --> 00:19:33.780
Arise!

213
00:19:38.810 --> 00:19:40.430
Damn it!

214
00:19:40.510 --> 00:19:46.030
Unless they undergo a reawakening.
a hunter's powers won't change.

215
00:19:46.110 --> 00:19:48.860
We have only two ways
to gain strength:

216
00:19:48.940 --> 00:19:52.970
Perfecting our techniques.
and gathering allies.

217
00:19:53.770 --> 00:19:56.040
Waiting for your king. are you?

218
00:19:56.120 --> 00:19:59.580
How can you be certain
he'll make his return?

219
00:19:59.660 --> 00:20:03.450
Knight Commander Igris.
you are a warrior.

220
00:20:03.530 --> 00:20:07.760
That means your purpose
is to cut down your foes.

221
00:20:07.840 --> 00:20:11.990
Will you let your blade
rust in this crumbling ruin?

222
00:20:12.630 --> 00:20:18.270
Or will you rise above
that fate and serve me?

223
00:20:18.350 --> 00:20:21.470
Instead of defending
the throne of a fallen king.

224
00:20:21.550 --> 00:20:24.850
Pledge yourself
to the man before you.

225
00:20:24.930 --> 00:20:27.010
Arise.

226
00:20:38.820 --> 00:20:43.700
Despite that. there's something I
like to envision from time to time.

227
00:20:55.540 --> 00:21:00.870
New hunters awaken each and
every day. all around the world.

228
00:21:02.180 --> 00:21:06.250
From now on. you are simply Igris.

229
00:21:07.850 --> 00:21:10.170
That is your name.

230
00:21:11.150 --> 00:21:15.230
So who's to say that someone
who defies all expectations.

231
00:21:15.310 --> 00:21:19.780
someone strong enough to become
a beacon of hope in these dark times.

232
00:21:19.860 --> 00:21:23.310
couldn't be born this very moment?

233
00:21:37.880 --> 00:21:39.910
You're with me now.

234
00:23:19.150 --> 00:23:22.150
Guild master. what is this?

235
00:23:22.230 --> 00:23:23.530
I don't know.

236
00:23:23.610 --> 00:23:27.160
To my knowledge. this
hasn't ever happened before.

237
00:23:27.240 --> 00:23:30.020
Somehow. it would seem.

238
00:23:31.950 --> 00:23:33.980
They're evolving.

239
00:23:34.305 --> 00:24:34.358
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm
